# Migration

This rules represents how database migration applied. Included : 
- What library used
- How migration file generated
- How miggration applied (up and down)


## Libraries 

The migration process utilize https://github.com/rubenv/sql-migrate library. All migration file stored in ``migration/`` directory

## How to generate migration file 

```bash
$ sql-migrate new <migration_name>
```

